Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:23.34,Yosuga,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\an4\bord0\shad0\fs36\c&H8B8C8A&\pos(730.5,373.5)\frz359.302\frx358\fry358}Còn lâu không?
